<h2 id="bkmrk-%E2%9C%85-part-4%3A-automate-w">✅ PART 4: Automate with <code>cron</code></h2>
<h3 id="bkmrk-%F0%9F%94%81-run-the-script-aut">🔁 Run the script automatically on a schedule</h3>
<ol id="bkmrk-open-crontab%3A">
<li>
<p>Open crontab:</p>
